           <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500/20 to-indigo-600/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition"><i data-lucide="upload" class="w-7 h-7 text-indigo-400"></i></div>
           <div class="font-mono text-indigo-400 text-xs mb-2">01</div>
           <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Upload CV Kamu</h3>
           <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Upload CV dan pilih posisi yang kamu lamar. AI kami akan menganalisis secara instan.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="scroll-reveal glass rounded-2xl p-8 text-center group hover:bg-white/[0.08] transition">
           <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500/20 to-purple-600/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition"><i data-lucide="mic" class="w-7 h-7 text-purple-400"></i></div>
           <div class="font-mono text-purple-400 text-xs mb-2">02</div>
           <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Latihan Interview AI</h3>
           <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Simulasi interview realistis sesuai role yang kamu pilih. Seperti interview sungguhan!</p>
          </div>
          <div class="scroll-reveal glass rounded-2xl p-8 text-center group hover:bg-white/[0.08] transition">
           <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500/20 to-pink-600/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition"><i data-lucide="bar-chart-3" class="w-7 h-7 text-pink-400"></i></div>
           <div class="font-mono text-pink-400 text-xs mb-2">03</div>
           <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Dapatkan Feedback Instan</h3>
           <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Evaluasi objektif soal kualitas jawaban, struktur, dan kepercayaan diri — langsung setelah latihan.</p>
          </div>
         </div>
        </div>
       </section>

       <section id="features" class="py-16 sm:py-24 relative bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-950 via-slate-900/50 to-slate-950">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
         <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16 scroll-reveal"><span class="inline-block text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-indigo-400 mb-3">Fitur Unggulan</span>
